[The state of Ohio can be located on the HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map at https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=4432007,7005. Ashtabula County, the northeast corner of Ohio, can be seen on the map at http://geology.com/county-map/ohio-county-map.gif. - Sr.Tech.Ed.MJ

The show veterinarian was closely involved in this case as the animals were sent home. To protect the other animals, and possibly for human protection this was likely a wise move.

Thus far, no humans from this particular fair have been reported with this strain of flu. Personal hygiene around animals is more than just a good idea; it is a great way to reduce the spread of any virus among animals or from animals to people - Mod.TG]
